accordionData.title: Can I use ellty for free?
accordionData.content: Yes of course you can use the free plan. You can choose to upgrade to the PRO plan to use premium features.

accordionData.title: Can I change my plan later?
accordionData.content: Yes! You can upgrade or cancel your subscription plan from within your account settings at any time.

accordionData.title: What can I design?
accordionData.content: You can create anything from social media templates to printable graphics.

accordionData.title: What payment options are available?
accordionData.content: We accept credit and debit cards: Visa, MasterCard, American Express, Discover and PayPal.

accordionData.title: Do I need to install anything?
accordionData.content: Nothing whatsoever! Ellty lives in the cloud so you can access your browser it on any Mac or desktop computer with an internet connection.

CategoriesPage.title: Instagram Post Templates

meta.description:
Ellty offers beautiful Instagram post templates to help you create beautiful,
high- quality posts. Whether you need a basic post template or something more creative, we
have you covered. Use our templates to create your next Instagram post.

CategoriesPage.text:
Choose ready-to-publish Instagram posts and create stunning ones with Ellty's
high-quality Instagram post templates to go viral on Instagram.

stripeBottom.title: Ellty's Instagram Post Templates
text: Ellty offers a library of eye-catching Instagram posts templates and layouts to help you create attractive, engaging Instagram photos as a professional. These templates come in various themes, colors, and styles, including food, travel, fashion, quotes, vintage,etc. Whether you're creating an Instagram post just for your personal use or using them to promote your business - we have the Perfect Template for You!

Instagram is a great way to connect with your followers individually and build your brand
by sharing photos and videos. To help you get the most out of your Instagram account,
we have a rich of the best Instagram post templates. These templates are created with
the same care and attention to detail that goes into our Instagram posts. They ensure
that every Instagram post you make is unique and enjoyable. So, what are you waiting

or? Let's get started. Pick our ready-to- use templates and customize them according to
your needs.

No matter what kind of Instagram post you want to create, we can help. With our
extensive selection of stunning and easy-to-customize Instagram post templates and
straightforward editing tools, we're happy to help you up to your Instagram game.

If you're looking for an easy way to create an Instagram post, look beyond our library of
templates. You can choose one and customize it with our drag-and-drop editing tools.
You can also change the colors, text, add images, and more!

CategoriesPage.title: Instagram Story Templates

meta.description:
dEllty offers designer-made Instagram story templates to help you
create an aesthetically pleasing and functional Instagram feed. With no design skills
necessary, get started today and see the difference for yourself

stripeBottom.title: Ellty's Instagram Stories Templates
text:
Instagram stories are a great way to keep your followers engaged with you and your
brand. They are also an excellent way for new followers to discover your account and
get involved with your community. You can use Instagram story templates to help your
brand stand out and get noticed on IG. Get the best Instagram stories templates here to
start improving your account and increase your followers’ engagement rate.

If you use Instagram as your primary social media platform, you’ve probably started to
notice an increase in the number of followers you are getting. And if you are like a lot of
other marketers, you might be wondering how you can start generating more
engagement from your followers and get them to follow back. The Instagram story will
help to get more attention. But you do not have any design skills or have no time to
create a creative design. Don’t worry! The good news for you is that Ellty offers
designer-made Instagram story templates to help you build aesthetically pleasing,
cohesive Instagram stories.

With Ellty’s collection of free Instagram story templates, you can create beautiful and
engaging stories in minutes. There are a lot of different Instagram story templates
available, so it can be hard to find one that’s perfect for your business. We have created
this collection of the most comprehensive and user-friendly Instagram story templates
that you can use to improve your account and increase your followers’ engagement
rate

With these templates, you have the freedom to create engaging stories for your
followers. It is so simple to edit and customize that it’s easy to get the look and feel you
want. The powerful editor makes creating your story quick and easy- drag and drop text
into place! Plus, with a vast media

library filled with unique illustrations, animations, images, frames, etc., there are endless
possibilities for what you can create!

CategoriesPage.text:
Whether you're a beginner or an experienced designer, our editable Instagram story
templates will help you create a cohesive and aesthetic Instagram feed. You can easily design
your own stories using powerful tools without any design skills.

CategoriesPage.title: Facebook Post Templates

meta.description:
With Ellty, you can easily create free Facebook post templates to match your
brand identity and occasion. Browse our selection of expertly curated templates to get started.

stripeBottom.title: Ellty's Facebook Post Templates
text:
If you are looking to stand out from the crowd, you need to use Facebook post
templates. They are the perfect way to get your message across in a unique way to you.
With so many different post templates, it cannot be easy to know where to begin.
Thankfully, Ellty has come to your aid with its massive collection of Facebook post
templates. Working with Ellty has been an absolute pleasure. So, what are you waiting
for? Get started with these top-notch post templates by Ellty and begin crafting the
perfect Facebook post.

When creating Facebook posts, it is important to make them easy on the eyes and
attract people's attention. This can be done by using our beautiful, customizable
templates and intuitive editing platform. All you need is a few simple steps: picking a
Facebook post template from our library, personalizing it as you see fit, then sharing it
on your page or profile!

Creating unique Facebook posts is not always easy - but with Ellty's help, it has never
been easier!

With Ellty you will never have to worry about having a good idea for your next post. Our
Facebook post templates will inspire you and help you come up with ideas that suit your
business needs and attract more customers!

With a wide range of Facebook post layouts and templates, Ellty has the perfect post for
you. Our collection of birthday-themed posts is tailored just for you, with fun and colorful
designs. Please scroll through our selection to find the perfect one for your message!
Do you have a specific post template design in mind? We've got plenty of them waiting
for you. Just browse through our library or until a particular template catches your eye.

After picking a template, you will be able to edit it. You can change the text and images
and even add videos, polls, or quizzes. The editing process is very straightforward and
intuitive - you will learn how to do it in no time. To make your Facebook posts stand out,
try adding a call-to- action button. For example, if you promote an event or a product,
you can add a button that says "Buy Now."

After you personalize your Facebook post, wait a few seconds for the changes to save,
then share it instantly on your page.

CategoriesPage.text:
Looking for a way to create professional-looking Facebook posts? Look no further than
our selection of expertly curated free Facebook post templates. With easy-to-use design tools,
you can easily customize any design to fit your occasion and brand identity. No design
experience or technical skills are required.

CategoriesPage.title: Pinterest Pin Templates

meta.description:
Customize your pins with Ellty, the easiest way to make your Pin look great!
Use our templates to make your Pin look unique and professional.

stripeBottom.title: Ellty's Pinterest Pin Templates
text:
Pinterest is a social network where people share and discover ideas. It's an amazing
resource for getting ideas for parties, dinners, and more. The best part is that you can
use Pinterest to promote your business without spending much money. There are many
different types of pins that you can create on Pinterest. You can create pins for special
events, beauty ideas, fashion, home décor, etc. You can also get creative and create
your boards to share with your followers. To stand out on Pinterest, you'll need to put
your creative skills and make your pins look amazing.
Pins are a type of design found on Pinterest. They're often used to share ideas, photos,
and other content. Pins can also be used to promote your business or to connect with
your followers.
With Ellty, you can easily create stunning Pinterest Pins with our high-quality and
creative graphic templates. Choose a pin template from the library and customize it
using our intuitive editing tools. You'll be able to use these templates to make unique
visual representations of your ideas, thoughts, and experiences!
Using our template editor, you can create beautiful graphic designs with ease. You can
resize or reposition elements in the design, switch up the colors, choose different font
pairings, and add images and graphics from our media library. You can also use your
photos by uploading them into the design.
Once you have selected a template from our collection, you can begin customizing it to
fit your needs. You can resize, reposition, and rearrange any of the elements in the
template. You can also change the colors of any element in the template using our color
picker tool. Additionally, you can add images from our extensive image library or upload
your pictures into the design.
When you are satisfied with how your graphic looks, you can download it as a JPG or
PNG file and use it as a Pinterest Pin!

CategoriesPage.text:
Explore and select our pre-designed Pinterest pin templates. With just a few clicks, you
can create a professional-looking Pinterest Pin right away using our easy-to-use editing
features. You can choose from a variety of text, images, and more to make your post look great.

CategoriesPage.title: Logo Templates

meta.description:
Get started with Ellty's free logo templates to create a unique, lasting
impression on your customers. With easy-to-use design tools and an abundance of icons, you'll
be able to create logos in minutes.

stripeBottom.title: Ellty's Logo Templates
text:
Do you ever feel unsure about starting a new business venture or when to start your
marketing campaign? Do you ever find it hard to develop new logo ideas for your
company? If so, you're in good company. As with any creative industry, the logo is no
exception. However, It cannot be easy to design a logo for your brand if you don't have
cultural familiarity with it. This takes time and resources that could be better spent
elsewhere.

So how do you get the right logo design if you don't know what it should look like? There
is no need to worry about that. If you're looking for a free logo maker that is intuitive and
easy to use, Ellty's is perfect. You won't have to pay for the designer or repeat
communication - all you need is an internet connection and a computer! With our simple
interface, you'll be able to make beautiful logos in minutes. Our rich icons and fonts will
help give your design lots of personality.

Don't worry; no design experience or ideas. Ellty offers a variety of logo templates to
help you create a beautiful and unique logo. With easy-to-use design tools and a large
selection of templates, you can create a logo that will stand out. We have a wide range
of pre-set logo samples that meet your needs.

Logos are a great way to brand your company and provide a strong connection with
your customers. You can easily customize them by choosing one from our logo
templates. The most important is that all your adjustments need to match the style and
image of your business. This is why we offer a variety of logo templates. You can use
any of them for your business, as long as it fits your company's style and image.

The logo is the reflection of any company. So, When designing a logo, it should be
adjusted together with the company name, goal, products, and the other required
element to represent the business. As a result, anyone can connect it to the brand or
business after noticing the logo.

To make your business more visible, you can choose a suitable logo template. The
uniqueness of the design depends on the company name and the colors. The color of
your logo should be appropriate to your brand and services.

CategoriesPage.text:
Use a unique logo to leave a lasting impression on your customers. With Ellty's free logo
